        "accordion_pane_RwQAXf": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do your swimsuits stay on in the surf?",
            "content": "<p>Our one pieces and long sleeve styles are specifically designed to feel secure and supportive in the water. The firm fit, contouring panels, and sculpting cuts are intended to minimise movement while surfing and swimming. For larger surf conditions, we generally recommend our more supportive one-piece styles for maximum coverage and security.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_QAHdEK": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes Ocean Soul Swimwear different?",
            "content": "<p>Ocean Soul Swimwear is designed specifically for women who want swimwear that feels secure, flattering, and comfortable while actually moving in and around the water. Our pieces are designed to stay in place while surfing, swimming, freediving, travelling, and long beach days — without sacrificing style or comfort. We use premium recycled Italian fabrics, sculpting panelled cuts, and UPF 50+ protection across much of the range</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_keU3mH": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is your swimwear designed for surfing and active use?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Our swimwear is created for active ocean lifestyles including surfing, swimming, freediving, paddleboarding, and travel. Many customers specifically choose Ocean Soul because they were frustrated with swimwear shifting, slipping, or needing constant adjusting in the water.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_CYhaY8": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are your swimsuits flattering?",
            "content": "<p>Flattering fit is one of the most common pieces of customer feedback we receive. Our designs use strategic paneling, contour lines, cinched waistbands, and sculpting fabric to help define the waist and create a streamlined silhouette.</p>"
          }
        }
